#

Avocado Hummus

10 min
$4.5
300 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

AppetizerHealthyDip

Description

Creamy and flavorful avocado hummus, perfect for dipping or spreading.

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • tahini: 1/4 cup
  • fresh lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • garlic: 1 clove
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • cumin: 1/2 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1/4 teaspoon
